page.title: 20CONCLUSION
page.content: The second year pupils of Kingsmead Comprehensive greatly enjoyed taking part in the project .Their final survey was of popular Christian names of their fellow pupils:Sarah was the most popular girl's name followed by Helen and Joanne:for the boys Mark was closely followed by Paul and Shaun. Those taking part were:- Samphire Bartholomew:Louise Branscomb: Ben Carter:Keenan Daw:Naomi Dennis: Andrew Donald:Erica Duffy: Christopher Eiserbeck:Nicholas Elkin: Jennifer Henson:Kevin Hims:Penny Noble Debbie Parsons:Sarah Pearce: Joanne Scott:Ian Somerfield: Andrew Trust:Stephen Woodward
